data.description: This unique corner-lot home is unlike any other in the neighborhood.  Enjoy spacious single-level living with an additional 1,080 square foot unfinished basement.  You’ll love the privacy that the split floorplan offers with 1 of 2 master suites on one end of the home, guest rooms and additional suite opposite end with the 5th bedroom centrally located making for a convenient office space. The great room provides the perfect place to gather whether it be in front of the rock hearth pellet-stove or in the dining area where the granite buffet countertop offers up a convenient place for food and drinks with numerous  dimmable recessed lighting throughout.  The basement has been used as a game room and place of relaxation that currently houses a ping/pong table, sauna, and wine cellar.   The perks continue as you enter and are greeted by a private secure courtyard with Trex decking.  Outback you can relax on the covered deck and enjoy the tankless pond fountain while watching the beautiful Northern Nevada sunsets or stay busy in the workshop that’s equipped with 220V and a rollup door.  Kids can enjoy a separate play in the shaded playhouse that sits on the side yard under apricot and cherry trees. Garage is deep 2.5 car with plenty of storage and a workbench.  There’s also room for RV parking on the side. Additional amenities include upgraded flooring throughout, interior, and exterior paint, granite kitchen countertops, newer appliances, pellet-stove, front and back Trex decking, remodeled bathrooms, new roof with 75% seamless gutters around, tankless water heater (gas & electric), garage door/controller, triple pane windows, INDOW windows in all bedrooms, N. and S. fences, greenhouse, hot tub circuit and solar.
